                <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> Cominius Cassia<supplied reason="lost">nus <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>atus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Augg</abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan></supplied> septizonium <expan><abbr>marmorib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> musaeo et omni cultu vetustate dilabsum <note>sic</note> restituit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>5 Fragmente eines Architravs, davon 4 aneinanderpassend, eines verschollen. Datierung: M. Aurelius Cominius Cassianus war 247/248 n. Chr. Statthalter in Numidien.</p>
